nt-Reznor-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Trent-Reznor-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Trent-Reznor-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Trent-Reznor-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Nine-Inch-Nails">九寸钉</a>与<a href="https://www.drmartens.com/us/en/collaborations/nine-inch-nails?utm_source=Instagram&amp;utm_medium=global_post&amp;utm_campaign=NIN_150724" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Dr. Martens</a>合作推出“The Downward Spiral”30 周年纪念靴系列。</p><p>此次合作于本月初首次曝光，并于今天（7 月 15 日）正式宣布。该鞋类系列将包括三双靴子和一双鞋子，其特色是该乐队获得格莱美提名的专辑中的艺术作品，以及受到九英寸钉乐队现场表演启发的设计。</p><p> Nine Inch Nails x Dr. Martens 系列将于本周五（7 月 19 日）在<a href="https://www.drmartens.com/us/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">drmartens.com</a>和指定零售商处发售。粉丝们可以<a href="https://www.drmartens.com/us/en/collaborations/nine-inch-nails?utm_source=Instagram&amp;utm_medium=global_post&amp;utm_campaign=NIN_150724" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处进行注册，</a>以便在收藏品到达时第一时间收到通知。</p><p>第一个款式是一款 1460 靴子，展示了 Russell Mills 的“Wound”艺术品，配有多种扣件，包括带有品牌标志的脚踝拉链。第二款是 1461 三眼鞋，展示了专辑的“Crystal Teeth”图像，带有微妙光泽的“<em>向下螺旋</em>”。第三款鞋款是 1490 10 眼靴子，灵感源自 NIN 玉米淀粉覆盖的现场表演。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C9cib5ZNyf_/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" b